# ===========================================
# .gitignore for .NET + Node.js (RentalOS)
# ===========================================

# ---- .NET ----
## Build outputs
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/
out/
publish/

## NuGet packages
*.nupkg
*.snupkg
**/[Pp]ackages/
!**/[Pp]ackages/build/
*.nuget.props
*.nuget.targets

## Visual Studio
.vs/
*.suo
*.user
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates
*.csproj.user
.idea/

## Rider
.idea/
*.DotSettings.user

## Crash dumps & logs
*.log
*.tmp
*.temp
crash.txt
error.txt
ServiceFabricBackup/

## Entity Framework migrations local DB
*.mdf
*.ldf

## dotnet secrets
secrets.json
appsettings.*.json
!appsettings.json
!appsettings.Development.json

## Test result
TestResults/
*.trx
coverage/
*.coverage
*.coveragexml

# ---- Node.js / Next.js ----
node_modules/
.next/
.nuxt/
dist/
build/
.cache/
.parcel-cache/
.turbo/

## Env files
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
.env.development.local
.env.test.local
.env.production.local

## Logs
logs/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
*.log

## Package managers
.pnp.js
.yarn/cache
.yarn/unplugged
.yarn/build-state.yml
.yarn/install-state.gz

## OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# ---- Docker ----
*.dockerignore

# ---- Misc ----
*.bak
*.swp
*~
ERRORS.md
